The song is meant to be like that. The feel is dark, grim, talks about chaos of an urban mind in a city! She did her part well! 
About the life part, I hope you've listened to Rahman's Jai Ho? It's the same girl who sang the song. 
The singer is supposed to instil interest in you by his/ her voice, not by his/her expressions! :)
